	<h1 class="title">“建筑奥斯卡”普利茨克奖得主的私人博物馆里都摆了什么？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/101857/small/101857.jpg?1429073860" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">谢舒敏 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-14 12:25:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13489/medium/13489.jpg?1439464438" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="13489" data-title="《“建筑奥斯卡”普利茨克奖得主的私人博物馆里都摆了什么？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13489/medium/13489.jpg?1439464438" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13489.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
